Package com.ontotext.gate.vr

Interface Summary
IFolder  
 

Class Summary
ClassNode Represents a single class node from the visualized ontology
Gaze Gaze is a Gazetteer VR capable of viewing and editing gazetteer lists, linear definitions (lists.def files), and mapping definitions (mappings between ontology classes and gazetteer lists).
MappingTreeView Mapping Tree View extends JTree in order to represent the mapping information.
OntoTreeModel A Tree Model used for the tree view of an ontology.
 

Exception Summary
GeneralEditorException A general editor exception
